The paper deals with the existence of Nash equilibria in partially observed stochastic games with mean field interactions. This topic is related to game theory (cs.GT), control theory (cs.SY), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and information theory (cs.IT). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
